munication overhead between components. Finally, we use a\ncase study from the manufacturing domain to experimentally demonstrate the\nbenefits of the proposed framework.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Apr 2020 03:57:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-14"}
