 exclusive processes or to\nsemi-inclusive deep inelastic scattering processes; ii) to the case where the\nfinal state interaction is considered through a Glauber approximation; iii) to\nfinite momentum transfer kinematics.\n  As a first test, the hadronic tensor is applied to obtain the nuclear\nstructure function F$_2^A$ and to evaluate the EMC effect for $^3He$ in the\nBjorken limit.\n  Encouraging results including only the two-body part of the light-front\nspectral function are presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Apr 2020 11:54:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-24"}
