 proved very adept at doing a\nsophisticated relative background subtraction in the MST space. This was needed\nto compare the experimental self emission images to the rad-MHD simulation\nimages.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Apr 2020 15:41:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Oct 2020 21:00:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-04"}
